---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us | Self Health Living">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative pt-20 pb-16 md:pt-32 md:pb-24 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-green-accent/5 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center px-6 relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center">
      <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-green-accent mb-4">Our Philosophy</span>
      <h1 class="font-display font-extrabold text-4xl sm:text-6xl text-white tracking-tight leading-none mb-6">
        Moving From <br />
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-green-accent to-[#4fd1c5]">
          Data to Direction
        </span>
      </h1>
      <p class="font-sans text-gray-400 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mb-8">
        We are living in an era of unprecedented health information. Smart rings track our sleep, watches count our steps, and blood panels list hundreds of biomarkers. Yet, we have never had less direction.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission Statement & Story -->
  <section class="py-16 border-t border-white/5 bg-[#0d0f11]/20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-white mb-6">Why We Built SelfHealth</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-300 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          SelfHealth was born out of frustration. When looking at laboratory blood test results, we are met with obscure abbreviations and reference ranges that induce anxiety rather than action. When we check our sleep stats, we see charts but no guidelines on how to sleep deeper to support muscle synthesis.
        </p>
        <p>
          We set out to build a platform that acts as a <strong>knowledgeable friend, not a doctor</strong>. Through our static guides and our iOS app assistant, <strong>Aliya</strong>, we translate complex health metrics into simple, plain-English steps.
        </p>
        <p>
          Whether it is resistance training to retain muscle mass after 40 (our <strong>Train</strong> pillar) or adding soluble fiber and protein pancakes to your breakfast (our <strong>Fuel</strong> pillar), we focus on actionable science that keeps you vital and strong as you age.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Core Values -->
  <section class="py-16 border-t border-white/5">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-white text-center mb-12">Our Core Standards</h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Standard 1 -->
        <div class="glass-card p-6 border border-white/5">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-green-accent/10 text-green-accent flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-md font-bold text-white mb-2">On-Device Privacy First</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            Your medical records are yours. The SelfHealth app processes health metrics on-device wherever possible, keeping your credentials secure and telling you clearly if something needs the cloud.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Standard 2 -->
        <div class="glass-card p-6 border border-white/5">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-green-accent/10 text-green-accent flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-md font-bold text-white mb-2">Science-Backed Content</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            We ignore fitness fads and quick-fix diets. Every protocol inside our Train and Fuel pillars is backed by clinical peer-reviewed research and translated into clear guidance.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Standard 3 -->
        <div class="glass-card p-6 border border-white/5">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-green-accent/10 text-green-accent flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-md font-bold text-white mb-2">Physician Collaboration</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            We don't replace doctors; we help you talk to them. Aliya compiles your biomarkers into clear, summarized PDFs that you can take straight to your next annual checkup.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
